# Personal workspace files — never commit these.
# If you instantiate the templates here (e.g. `cp templates/*.md .`),
# these patterns keep your real resume / job / story data out of git.
/resume.md
/jobs.md
/story.md
/drained-log.md
/resume-hardened.md
/orchestrator.md

# Obsidian / editor / OS
.obsidian/
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# Claude Code local state (don't commit session or project state)
.claude/projects/
.claude/sessions/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/session-env/
